input.name: Mouse Hippocampal Sharp Wave Ripple Dataset from Public Neuropixels Datasets
input.citation: Mouse Hippocampal Sharp Wave Ripple Dataset from Public Neuropixels Datasets (2024). (Version draft) [Data set]. DANDI archive. https://dandiarchive.org/dandiset/001081/draft
input.description: Here we present the SWR data from the ABI and IBL datasets in a sharable format, which integrates with their APIs.  We have extracted, curated using field standards, and shared over 2,054,021 SWR events from 258 mice from these datasets as well as the code used to process them. Foundation Grant FDN-143209 and project grant PJT-180631
